com.scs.stevetech1.netmessages

Class EntityKilledMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.scs.stevetech1.netmessages.MyAbstractMessage
      • com.scs.stevetech1.netmessages.EntityKilledMessage

  • public class EntityKilledMessage
extends MyAbstractMessage
    This is used to inform the client that an entity has been killed. If the entity killer or "killee" is an avatar, the client can inform the player. The client should also remove the rigid body from the entity.
